import { Box, Container, Stack } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'

function StorePage() {
  
  return (
    <Container>
     <Stack
  direction="column-reverse"
  justifyContent="center"
  alignItems="flex-start"
  spacing={2}
>
  <Stack>
 Product Types
  </Stack>
 
  </Stack>


    </Container>
  )
}

export default StorePage
